item.title: 1488.Avoid Flood in The City-避免城市的洪水
item.description: 问题描述 Your country has an infinite number of lakes. Initially, all the lakes are empty, but when it rains over the nth lake, the nth lake becomes full of water. item.title: 1481. Least Number of Unique Integers after K Removals-K清除后的不同元素的最小个数
item.description: 问题描述 Given an array of integers arr and an integer k. Find the least number of unique integers after removing exactly k elements. Example: Input: arr = [5,5,4], k = 1 Output: 1 解题思路 这道题目求解在数组中去除k个元素后所剩余的不同元素的最小值。
